room_title: Escape room "T.A.C.O. Tuesday" by Unlocked! Escape Rooms in Andover
room_description: You are Agent Tuesday of the Tex-Mex American Cuisine Organization (T.A.C.O.). Your mission is to infiltrate the headquarters of a supervillain who has stolen a legendary hot sauce as part of his complicated, but totally plausible, evil scheme to make an irresistible taco that will enable him to take over the world!
